MobileMultiscreen

Basic Concept:
Connect Mobilephones to a http server and send out information for coloring the screen dependend on location.
This should create a massive screen for concerts or gatherings of peoples.

Restrictions:
Handeling thousend of connections needs a reliable, minimal overhead comunication.
Possisioning is hard, gps and wlan triangulation are unrelaaiable. Image scan or manual configuration could be a solution.
Have all the devices insync will be difficult
